Output demo/segments/segment2-streaming.mp4
Output demo/segments/segment2-streaming.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1500
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 12

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

